title: Luna Rotisserie & Empanadas
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Latin American, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu influence is South American meets American South. Uses local ingredients when possible. Vegan items are labeled and include jackfruit grain bowl which comes with chili-braised jackfruit, quinoa, pearled barley, black beans, kale, and topped with guacamole. Full bar with specialty cocktails, plus non-alcoholic made-in-house aguas frescas.
